name: CobaltMIPS cpu
tagline: Parametric, superscalar, out-of-order execution, Tomasulo-based MIPS cpu
body:
### Welcome to CobaltMIPS cpu
CobaltMIPS is microprocessor based in MIPS instruction set but with a simpler architecture. It supports nice features like:
* Superscalar execution units
* Out-of-order instruction dispatching
* Tomasulo-based architecture
* Fully parametric
